{"tid":448310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【河馬比港豬更團結】鱷魚想突襲河馬B 被超過30隻進擊的河馬圍攻","createTime":"2017-10-26T05:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T04:53:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2c79019e09134547fda55deb9374848c2e1e3a","tid":448310,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171025/large/1508917463_de7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171025%2Flarge%2F1508917463_de7c.jpg&h=ee1bddac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坦桑尼亞東北部塞倫蓋蒂（Serengeti）有鱷魚非常猖狂，竟然深入河馬地盤妄想突襲河馬寶寶，結果被一群逾30隻河馬包圍，最後落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\n這一幕由71歲退休攝影師庫瑪（Harish Kumar）旅行時拍到，當時超過30隻河馬圍住一隻鱷魚，將牠按入水中，而2隻河馬寶寶則被其他河馬好好保護着。當鱷魚在2隻寶寶身邊再次上水時，其中一隻成年河馬立即咬向鱷魚。<br />\n<br />\n庫瑪表示：「導遊帶我們到一個叫河馬池的地方&hellip;&hellip;我們只是周圍看看，突然間太太叫住我說有事發生了，當時池內有一大群河馬。」<br />\n<br />\n他直言非常幸運可以拍下這一幕，「那隻鱷魚竟然可以游走在一群憤怒的河馬間，這些河馬想要牠立即離開地盤，河馬人多勢眾，鱷魚被拋來拋去又被咬，但牠幸運地在沒有受傷的情況下離開。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"011c8bbe07efd85c141465e68136687f1bf77684","tid":448310,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"點解要咁暴力<br />\n<br />\n鱷魚都係為左生存  有阿爸阿媽生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67e0065d056cb99a4a9bffb5191b6786b2e769c","tid":448310,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"仲以為隻鱷魚死硬....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6257e86db99380ccf51c71153c13630f75eeee","tid":448310,"uid":56661,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2En5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2En5a.jpg&h=ccffca3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"502118c1b23df2815373622cc1d862f97a0f8f20","tid":448310,"uid":21461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"真正晒馬"},{"pid":"1cfe780bed35172945c4eea1f8d12f5dab5b8b1d","tid":448310,"uid":9708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"呢度30人 一人爆你一個可樂樽都幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13e0e61fad204dab279ceb9befaa3a20e9bd794","tid":448310,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛比連登仔更團結</span></strong>"},{"pid":"aab5f4a77eb721c40ae24bfb9515da7c1acd66d5","tid":448310,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"不嬲河馬都可以係好危險動物<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇外表以為好蝦"},{"pid":"52bdc7abf44adef5daaeff4c1756288a15cdbef0","tid":448310,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"一打三十仲可以全身以退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67e20adb0d0462f941a159e7e937d9287b2e11b","tid":448310,"uid":106641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲河馬都可以係好危險動物<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇外表以為好蝦</blockquote><br />\n河馬其實脾氣好臭而且智商低，好有地域性嘅動物嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時年幼河馬誤闖其他河馬嘅地盤遭受攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8202ee595f52fa16ca8f1c4275a1cff38216b99e","tid":448310,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"非洲最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ea1757ce6d08df255673099cbb991d2d8ffc25","tid":448310,"uid":46279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"條片有無10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab89bd28cc7b36b3838874dc708d02dd9e5db039","tid":448310,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲河馬都可以係好危險動物<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇外表以為好蝦</blockquote><br />\n河馬年中咬／撞死唔少人"},{"pid":"63712f8c5852a870075ede03a8d5273165cb7a2d","tid":448310,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"被河馬咬都可以無受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779279d2032e50ca57c4ce39e2d47dcf34396ee3","tid":448310,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m4ndsfay\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm4ndsfay&h=7ff698e6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}